Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和恙神涯在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照『藍、藍、紅』的順序按下按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我們就可以給他們處以相應的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論他們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.67,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在昏睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是被抽了虛空後受到衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:17.90,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道什麼時候才能醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我來重新介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是櫻滿集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有虛空基因組的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.63,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(556,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將以集為中心展開作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過櫻滿集的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和城戶研二的獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們葬儀社當今最大的目標{\fscx200}－
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白血球的攻略將是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白血球？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作戰方案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據狀況不同模式分歧為145個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動之前 全員都要把這些全部記在腦子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連這也做不到的話  就別參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊隔離設施的任務到現在還不到一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心大家會很疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是為了什麼來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了好好休養
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想帶著還被眼屎模糊了的視野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼懶散地出現在敵人面前嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這傢伙進行能適應這次作戰的基礎訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到現在為止只是個累贅而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還珍惜自己的性命的話就好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 其實不用管我也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果給輪椅女添很多麻煩的話 我很過意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還真是體貼呀 櫻滿同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我集就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪椅就是我的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你來同情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 真的要跳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來啊 相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服 還有筆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間再去睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想給你訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為涯說了我才過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你到底為什麼要來葬儀社的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合適也要有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼 是個好東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到個好主意了 真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定一週後會測試你適不適合成為葬儀社的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能及格的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就還˙給˙你～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是龍泉高中2年級的月島阿爾戈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用真心想殺人的心情來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬儀社的名字可是很沉重的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的就害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳次數正以令人驚奇的速度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平時多不愛運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是文科生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼樣啊 大雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這方面 還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要以此為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話會磨破手指的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拇指再過來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太親近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.39,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\b1\shad0\bord0\frx0\fry12\frz20.997\pos(496,361)\c&H000000&}色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很順利呢 白血球計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的籠子 我很喜歡這種惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多嘴 你丟下的楔子怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的機率是五成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾戈 集 請這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這次是和涯一起 小京？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 終於能一起作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看不到模擬戰有些遺憾  集 請加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼年輕的孩子都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 大家都會追崇那些有自信的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我 即使做一樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼人會認同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 在這個世界上任意妄為的人才能有所作為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯可不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 你以後能不能明白都很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你不覺得你這樣對我和涯是很無禮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空是無論從誰那裡都能取出的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.46,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼努力 搞得好像我真的要加入他們一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.54,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}「かぜが　なびいて」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:10:01.52,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}「ふたつ　かさなって」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:11.27,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}「生きた証を　私は唄おう」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:23.23,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}「名もなき者のため」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.54,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(100,150)}「風吹過」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:10:01.52,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(100,150)}「合二為一」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:11.27,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(100,150)}「我將歌頌生存的證據」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:23.23,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(100,150)}「為了那些無名之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像是我們第一次見面的時候呢 有些懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈 為什麼要加入葬儀社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是為什麼來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各種各樣的原因 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的可能是我很高興 那個時候 你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興那時你能來到我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 祈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 我說如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要你一起離開葬儀社的話 你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯賜予了我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字賜予了什麼都沒有的我 把世界給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的東西 要在一起 那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要太親近我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人一廂情願 真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都覺得涯很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走路不長眼睛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了那個房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡祈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節哀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人啊  每個月2、3次就像這樣共度夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都裝作沒看到其實都明白的 真遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨也覺得無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡涯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒證據在亂說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜不喜歡的問題 我很尊敬涯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 為什麼都說涯很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能認為這是女生都喜歡這樣硬派的帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道我可能是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概因為我還是個孩子 什麼都還不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想知道的話 就先取得明天模擬戰的勝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的話你就會被作為同伴而被認同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話肯定會明白一些事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定不再依賴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一個人爬起來又顯得不是很優雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不希望別人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越像那個女人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個中隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預定的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OAU和Leave Nations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛講規矩的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始模擬戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白血球攻略作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以腳本D-14為基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預想你不得不單人與人形兵器對峙的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:33.95,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(717,665)}endrave
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功擺脫steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進我身後的車輛裡 就是你的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是彩彈中了也會昏迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請認真一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是太難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都躲不掉綾瀨的人形兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:59.72,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(825,665)}endrave
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且steiner就更快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾姐 可以接續了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 Ready？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還敢背對我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃跑的樣子真是難看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要只靠自己是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 這麼悠哉悠哉可是會掛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾戈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我耍詐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啊 你只是發揮了你的個性而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籠罩黑暗的手電筒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的是個腹黑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你 集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從今天開始就是我們的夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的東西 下次別再弄丟好好保管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夥伴遊戲？ 真是開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒過來了嗎 研二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研二？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶研二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你從第四隔離設施裡救出來的人哦 集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫好夥伴遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是散漫啊 各種意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯那傢伙在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白血球向代爾塔地區發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯所在的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以3%的出力發射成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標破壞率 110%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤差為0.8m
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我進入萬劫不復的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來的人們，你們必須把一切希望拋開！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（出自但丁神曲）



